ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺點 : <br />\n1) 隻game岩岩出，好多評測都未有，到底咩武器最正，咩裝備最好，大家都仲試緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手自己摸索下<br />\n2)樓主自己都係新手，未必分析得好好，純粹用新手角度話俾1516既人聽，應唔應該買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfae5bd458397efc3bd70d14beb04193c46da020","tid":2463934,"uid":233316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"買就買數位，買實體就食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90eeab95ba5e398df1d58b7aa5ee1d32f36ea4","tid":2463934,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"pc 幾時有"}]}